data.description: Welcome to this lovingly updated & maintained home in Hilliard Green (the trifecta of location, Columbus taxes and Hilliard schools!). Take the time to appreciate the new garage & front door before being welcomed by the fresh paint and new LVP floors.  The main floor feels spacious as you stand in the updated kitchen (backsplash is only a few weeks old, and fridge and stove are '20) looking to the family room.  The fireplace in the will be warm & cozy as we move into winter - and it can be either gas or wood-burning.  Buyer's choice!  The oversized back deck is a perfect extension of the home, especially with the new privacy fence around the entire yard.  Upstairs, find a newly updated primary bath, vaulted ceilings in the primary, and 2 more spacious bdrms.  Schedule today!
